data.title: Washington University in St Louis: Costs, Jobs, Bar Results
data.meta_description: Washington University in St Louis overview on law school tuition, debt, salaries, enrollment, lawyer jobs, bar pass rates, and more. Washington University in St Louis currently enrolls a total of 809 students in their JD program. With an acceptance rate of 17.2%, they welcomed 244 new 1Ls in 2023 with a median LSAT of 173. Tuition and fees are $67.8k annually. Cost of living is estimated at $26.1k.
